snippet.title: Space Eater Force (Pretty Girls Stuffing Simulator)  release
snippet.description:
so, i decided to add some shoot em up  elements to the game so it is a little bit more interesting ,  it's now a game where you battle to get food and  eat food to level up in battle 

you can play it here:
